# Luxe Shine — environment variables
# Copy to .env.local for local dev; set the same keys in Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables.

# Mapbox public token (pk.*) — powers the address autocomplete in the "My Home" quote tab.
# Public tokens are meant to be exposed client-side; restrict it by URL in the Mapbox
# dashboard (Account → Tokens → URL restrictions) to your production + preview domains.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ vars are inlined at BUILD time, so set it in Vercel and redeploy.
# If unset, the address field degrades gracefully to a plain input (no live dropdown).
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN=
